## Pre-requisites on CentOS

Install pre-requisites on CentOS before running `gem install` commands:

```
sudo yum install gcc ruby ruby-devel mysql-devel postgresql-devel postgresql-libs sqlite-devel libxslt-devel libxml2-devel yajl-ruby
```

## Installing AWS Boostrap CLI (optional)

Run this command to install additional AWS bootstrap commands:

```
gem install bosh_cli_plugin_aws
```
